name: Makeup Bod
short_description:
The heart of an attractive appearance is derived by management of the original face shape, contour and highlight specific regions of the face with makeup, hairstyles and accessories. Learn to acquire symmetry and shape eyebrows to emit character within the realms of beauty, an activity for all ages and both genders.
Follow the steps outlined to learn the art of a made up face and use the template provided to create your own personality with your acquired knowledge of how makeup colours can be used in harmony with skin colour and tone, eye and hair colour and attire.
summary: Step by step guide to equal proportioned and symmetrical appearance.
